was definitely sent by them.

86
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:47,630
Lingfeng,

87
00:03:48,750 --> 00:03:50,120
you're our only hope

88
00:03:50,470 --> 00:03:51,870
in the Hero Gathering.

89
00:03:51,870 --> 00:03:52,840
Don't worry,

90
00:03:53,030 --> 00:03:54,910
I won't let them succeed.

91
00:03:55,910 --> 00:03:56,870
You've seen

92
