the Imperial Court.

99
00:04:19,230 --> 00:04:20,200
Lingfeng,

100
00:04:20,590 --> 00:04:22,120
you're brave and talented.

101
00:04:22,230 --> 00:04:23,810
So, among the heroes in the association,

102
00:04:25,030 --> 00:04:26,310
I only trust you.

103
00:04:26,630 --> 00:04:27,470
Uncle Wu,

104
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:29,720
I've always seen you as my role model.

105
00:04:29,950 --> 00:04:32,070
No matter how the association changes,

106
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:34,070
I will always trust you.

107
00:04:37,190 --> 00:04:38,120
Okay.

108
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:39,480
I knew I was right about you.

109
00:04:40,270 --> 00:04:41,270
Don't worry,

110
00:04:41,270 --> 00:04:43,720
I'll help you get the hero token.

111
00:04:44,510 --> 00:04:45,350
However,

112
00:04:45,750 --> 00:04:47,270
Eunuch Deng has forbidden

113
00:04:47,270 --> 00:04:48,830
the use of demonic skills.

114
00:04:49,630 --> 00:04:50,470
Well...

115
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:52,000
Don't worry about that.

116
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:53,950
I have a plan.

117
00:04:54,630 --> 00:04:55,480
Really?

118
00:04:56,070 --> 00:04:57,000
Of course.

119
00:04:58,120 --> 00:05:00,120
But the Hero Gathering is coming,

120
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:02,510
and all forces will try to get
what they want.

121
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:04,190
You must stay clear-headed.

122
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:05,360
During this time,

123
00:05:05,630 --> 00:05:07,720
don't let anyone manipulate you.

124
00:05:08,430 --> 00:05:09,560
Don't worry.

125
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:30,040
It's not working.

126
00:05:31,310 --> 00:05:32,680
It's not working at all.

127
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:44,880
Did you forget?

128
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,870
I'm your living remedy.

129
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:52,240
Why are you here?

130
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:54,680
I knew you'd need me,

131
00:05:54,870 --> 00:05:56,160
so I came.

132
00:05:56,390 --> 00:05:57,230
But...

133
00:05:58,000 --> 00:06:00,160
the Hero Gathering is coming.

134
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:02,000
You can't lose blood now.

135
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:03,240
Yes,

136
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:04,920
the Hero Gathering is important,

137
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:06,200
but

138
00:06:07,070 --> 00:06:08,480
you're far more important.

139
00:06:12,070 --> 00:06:12,910
Let's go home.

140
00:06:36,390 --> 00:06:37,230
Yingdan,

141
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:38,630
you're awake.

142
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,310
You idiot.

143
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:46,510
If you don't feel well,

144
00:06:46,510 --> 00:06:47,680
you must tell me.

145
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:48,600
As long as I'm here,

146
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:50,830
I won't let you suffer from the recoil.

147
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:55,480
Thank you.

148
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:57,800
Don't be so polite to me.

149
00:06:58,430 --> 00:07:00,720
You really don't
take care of yourself at all.

150
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,630
The recoil was fierce,

151
00:07:03,070 --> 00:07:04,070
yet you faced it alone.

152
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:06,000
If I hadn't discovered it,

153
00:07:06,510 --> 00:07:07,630
anything could happen.

154
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,360
From now on,

155
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:13,120
you can't leave me

156
00:07:13,750 --> 00:07:14,870
for more than two hours.

157
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:22,830
Yingdan, I just want you

158
00:07:23,390 --> 00:07:24,800
to relax and be

159
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:26,480
a carefree child

160
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:27,830
when you're with me.

161
00:07:28,190 --> 00:07:30,240
You can laugh and cry

162
00:07:30,430 --> 00:07:32,950
whenever you want to.

163
00:07:33,510 --> 00:07:34,750
You can cry on my shoulder.

164
00:07:34,750 --> 00:07:35,720
I'm here for you.

165
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:36,560
Okay?

166
00:07:52,830 --> 00:07:53,670
Master.

167
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:56,000
Gou.

168
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:57,480
How's Yingdan doing?

169
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:58,320
She's fine now.

170
00:07:58,330 --> 00:07:59,560
She's fallen asleep.

171
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:00,640
That's good.

172
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:01,840
Master.

173
00:08:02,070 --> 00:08:03,630
Focus on the Hero Gathering.

174
00:08:03,630 --> 00:08:05,830
Ling'er and I will take care of Yingdan.

175
00:08:06,400 --> 00:08:07,720
Eunuch Deng alone

176
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:10,000
