177
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:11,920
If Prince Chang meddles in,

178
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:13,830
who knows what will happen?

179
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:15,630
That's not true.

180
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:17,070
My father would never

181
00:08:17,070 --> 00:08:18,430
- stir up conflict.
- Your Highness.

182
00:08:18,430 --> 00:08:19,390
Your Highness,

183
00:08:19,390 --> 00:08:20,230
it's late.

184
00:08:20,230 --> 00:08:21,480
What brings you here?

185
00:08:23,510 --> 00:08:24,870
Now you know

186
00:08:24,870 --> 00:08:26,920
who controls the association, right?

187
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:28,800
You're family,

188
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:30,120
so don't pretend to take our side.

189
00:08:30,310 --> 00:08:32,240
