to marry Deng Yunfeng

190
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:34,240
just to work with Eunuch Deng

191
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:35,720
to control the association.

192
00:08:36,040 --> 00:08:38,040
It's not that simple.

193
00:08:38,040 --> 00:08:39,600
I don't know who's in power,

194
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:40,870
but I trust the chairman.

195
00:08:42,270 --> 00:08:44,440
If I tell you he won't be the chairman

196
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:45,910
after the Hero Gathering,

197
00:08:45,910 --> 00:08:47,720
do you still want to follow him?

198
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:49,240
What do you mean?

199
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:51,720
As you can see,

200
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:54,390
the association has many problems.

201
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:57,150
The so-called imperial court oversight

202
00:08:57,150 --> 00:08:58,080
was just a way

203
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:59,510
to control the forces

204
00:08:59,510 --> 00:09:00,910
in the martial world.

205
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:03,360
However, the oversight

206
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:05,150
seems to have changed.

207
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:06,550
With just an imperial edict,

208
00:09:06,870 --> 00:09:09,390
the rules of the Hero Gathering
can be changed.

209
00:09:10,750 --> 00:09:12,510
Is this really an oversight?

210
00:09:12,910 --> 00:09:13,750
Moreover,

211
00:09:14,150 --> 00:09:15,080
lately,

212
00:09:15,270 --> 00:09:17,720
many strange events
have happened in Huizhou,

213
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:19,670
yet they always turned out to be

214
00:09:19,670 --> 00:09:22,440
related to the association
or the demonic sect.

215
00:09:23,670 --> 00:09:25,510
Is this really just a coincidence?

216
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:27,750
I know our association
has many problems,

217
00:09:27,750 --> 00:09:28,670
but I believe

218
00:09:28,670 --> 00:09:30,790
Chairman Wu is trying to

219
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:32,030
improve it.

220
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:34,030
And I will help him

221
00:09:34,030 --> 00:09:36,150
to build a new association.

222
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:39,790
- Your Highness.
- Yingdan.

223
00:09:39,790 --> 00:09:41,030
What are you trying to say?

224
00:09:41,270 --> 00:09:42,320
Why are you here?

225
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:45,150
Floral Knight, you're here.

226
00:09:45,790 --> 00:09:47,240
Now that we have a smart person,

227
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:48,270
things will be easier.

228
00:09:49,550 --> 00:09:50,510
Recently,

229
00:09:50,510 --> 00:09:52,600
I've got a lot of suspicious intel.

230
00:09:52,790 --> 00:09:54,240
I was worried you might be deceived,

231
00:09:54,510 --> 00:09:56,670
so I came here to share it with you.

232
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:58,000
Your Highness,

233
00:09:58,240 --> 00:10:00,270
we're not interested in your intel.

234
00:10:00,270 --> 00:10:01,110
Ling'er.

235
00:10:02,750 --> 00:10:03,590
Let her speak.

236
00:10:05,150 --> 00:10:06,270
As far as I know,

237
00:10:06,670 --> 00:10:08,480
every officer in the association

238
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:11,000
must be strictly reviewed
by the chairman.

239
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:12,510
Back then,

240
00:10:12,510 --> 00:10:14,200
the vice chairman

241
00:10:14,390 --> 00:10:16,550
was actually the head
of the Alchemy Division,

242
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:18,550
and during his tenure,

243
00:10:18,550 --> 00:10:20,390
he maintained connections
with the demonic sect.

244
00:10:20,390 --> 00:10:21,550
As the chairman,

245
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:24,120
how could he not know

246
00:10:24,390 --> 00:10:26,550
such a serious situation?

247
00:10:26,550 --> 00:10:27,870
That was because

248
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:29,360
he wasn't in Huizhou

249
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:30,320
but in the Imperial City.

250
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:31,750
There were many internal affairs

251
00:10:31,750 --> 00:10:32,790
that he didn't know.

252
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:35,200
The Alchemy Division
also took advantage of this

253
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:36,670
and acted so brazenly.

254
00:10:38,270 --> 00:10:39,110
Okay.

255
00:10:39,550 --> 00:10:40,750
Maybe that's true.

256
00:10:41,390 --> 00:10:42,440
Then let's

257
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:44,240
talk about Puppet Knight.

258
00:10:44,910 --> 00:10:46,080
As far as I know,

259
00:10:46,630 --> 00:10:48,870
the Imperial Court never issued an order

260
00:10:48,870 --> 00:10:51,150
to hunt Puppet Knight,

261
00:10:51,150 --> 00:10:52,910
yet He Changzai still insisted

262
00:10:52,910 --> 00:10:54,360
on executing him on the spot.

263
00:10:55,390 --> 00:10:56,320
Who

264
00:10:56,750 --> 00:10:58,790
wanted to kill him so badly?

265
00:10:58,790 --> 00:10:59,750
Your Highness,

266
00:11:00,030 --> 00:11:01,480
it was chaotic at the time.

267
00:11:01,490 --> 00:11:02,390
Besides,

268
00:11:02,390 --> 00:11:04,360
He Changzai is an opportunist,

269
00:11:04,630 --> 00:11:05,630
so this

270
00:11:05,960 --> 00:11:07,150
doesn't prove much.

271
00:11:08,750 --> 00:11:09,750
Mr. Zhuge,

272
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:13,080
