274
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:18,080
Even if Zhuge Xun was bold,

275
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:19,960
would he dare to act alone

276
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:21,480
to seize power and rebel?

277
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:23,270
Unless

278
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:25,320
someone was

279
00:11:25,910 --> 00:11:27,270
pulling the strings

280
00:11:27,790 --> 00:11:28,720
and

281
00:11:28,910 --> 00:11:30,670
provided enough support for him.

282
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:32,840
