00:11:39,550 --> 00:11:41,360
I've told you so much.

286
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:43,000
I'm sure you have

287
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:44,550
your answer, right?

288
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:47,320
These cases have been solved,

289
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:48,870
and you're bringing them up now.

290
00:11:48,870 --> 00:11:51,030
Don't you have selfish intentions?

291
00:11:51,030 --> 00:11:52,910
You can say that,

292
00:11:52,910 --> 00:11:54,840
but I am not stirring up conflict.

293
00:11:55,510 --> 00:11:58,150
The Martial Artists Association
is under my father's command,

294
00:11:58,480 --> 00:11:59,670
and it was my father

295
00:11:59,670 --> 00:12:01,270
who promoted Wu Guangming.

296
00:12:01,790 --> 00:12:04,270
Whatever Wu Guangming can offer you,

297
00:12:04,870 --> 00:12:06,200
my father can do the same.

298
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:07,120
Your Highness,

299
00:12:07,120 --> 00:12:08,550
what exactly do you want?

300
00:12:08,910 --> 00:12:10,480
I just don't want everything

301
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:12,000
to be so chaotic.

302
00:12:12,390 --> 00:12:14,630
If you truly care about the association,

303
00:12:14,870 --> 00:12:16,550
why not fight for my father

304
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:18,600
and the association?

305
00:12:19,150 --> 00:12:20,030
Ridiculous.

306
00:12:20,550 --> 00:12:21,840
I am fighting for the chairman

307
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:23,550
and the association.

308
00:12:23,550 --> 00:12:26,000
What's the difference?

309
00:12:28,200 --> 00:12:29,910
Gou Lingfeng,

310
00:12:30,390 --> 00:12:31,870
after all I've told you,

311
00:12:31,870 --> 00:12:34,150
have you truly understood nothing?

312
00:12:34,440 --> 00:12:35,720
Wu Guangming

313
00:12:35,720 --> 00:12:37,600
is not someone
you can easily see through.

314
00:12:37,600 --> 00:12:39,000
He's manipulative.

315
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:42,870
Stop trying to persuade me
to work for Prince Chang.

316
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:44,800
Okay.

317
00:12:46,550 --> 00:12:48,270
Then let me ask you, Mr. Zhuge.

318
00:12:48,670 --> 00:12:49,600
Mr. Zhuge.

319
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:50,440
Your Highness.

320
00:12:50,790 --> 00:12:53,440
The Sword Alliance has always been
under Eunuch Deng's control.

321
00:12:54,240 --> 00:12:56,630
Now that it's in a great crisis,

322
00:12:57,120 --> 00:13:00,120
has Eunuch Deng ever stepped in

323
00:13:00,390 --> 00:13:02,440
to help resolve your trouble?

324
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:04,750
If my father is in charge of
the Sword Alliance,

325
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:06,440
he would never

326
00:13:06,440 --> 00:13:08,270
turn a blind eye.

327
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:09,670
Your Highness,

328
00:13:09,670 --> 00:13:11,360
stop turning us against each other.

329
00:13:11,750 --> 00:13:12,750
Ms. Ling'er,

330
00:13:13,720 --> 00:13:16,240
do you truly love Mr. Zhuge?

331
00:13:16,670 --> 00:13:17,910
What have you given him?

332
00:13:17,910 --> 00:13:18,870
Wealth,

333
00:13:18,870 --> 00:13:19,750
power,

334
00:13:20,150 --> 00:13:21,030
or betrayal?

335
00:13:21,030 --> 00:13:22,440
Your Highness, what do you mean?

336
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:23,440
Your Highness,

337
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:24,630
don't talk to her like that.

338
00:13:26,550 --> 00:13:27,600
Mr. Zhuge,

339
00:13:28,270 --> 00:13:30,240
my father and I can help you

340
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:32,630
resolve the urgent crisis
of the Sword Alliance.

341
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:34,840
I hope you can consider this.

342
00:13:35,630 --> 00:13:36,510
Don't worry.

343
00:13:36,870 --> 00:13:38,390
I don't force others to comply,

344
00:13:38,870 --> 00:13:40,670
nor do I ask for any sacrifice from you.

345
00:13:40,960 --> 00:13:41,910
I only hope

346
00:13:41,910 --> 00:13:42,960
if my father and I

347
00:13:42,960 --> 00:13:44,360
ever need the Sword Alliance's help,

348
00:13:44,360 --> 00:13:46,080
you can remember our kindness

349
00:13:46,080 --> 00:13:47,360
and lend us a helping hand.

350
00:13:47,630 --> 00:13:48,510
Heng,

351
00:13:48,720 --> 00:13:49,790
don't trust her.

352
00:13:50,960 --> 00:13:51,800
Okay.

353
00:13:52,240 --> 00:13:53,670
I've said enough.

354
00:13:53,670 --> 00:13:54,720
I think it's clear.

355
00:13:55,150 --> 00:13:57,550
I hope you can make a decision.

356
00:13:58,120 --> 00:13:59,550
This year's Hero Gathering

357
00:13:59,870 --> 00:14:02,030
will be a great show.

358
00:14:10,040 --> 00:14:10,910
Heng,

359
00:14:10,910 --> 00:14:12,360
don't trust her words!

360
00:14:12,360 --> 00:14:13,440
She just said

361
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:15,670
she and Prince Chang

362
00:14:15,670 --> 00:14:17,480
can solve the Sword Alliance's problem.

363
00:14:18,510 --> 00:14:19,350
Ling'er,

364
00:14:19,960 --> 00:14:21,390
once the problem is solved,

365
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:23,030
we can finally get married.

366
00:14:24,120 --> 00:14:25,000
Zhuge,

367
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:27,510
you must think about it carefully.

368
00:14:27,870 --> 00:14:28,910
I thought about it

369
00:14:30,080 --> 00:14:31,030
before.

370
00:14:31,550 --> 00:14:33,200
If we rely on other people's help,

371
00:14:33,200 --> 00:14:35,510
it won't address the root
of the problem.

372
00:14:36,030 --> 00:14:37,750
The Sword Alliance must rely on itself.

373
00:14:40,360 --> 00:14:41,200
Lingfeng.

374
00:14:42,720 --> 00:14:43,670
I think

375
00:14:44,510 --> 00:14:46,320
Princess Linglong had a point.

376
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:47,960
I've thought about everything she said.

377
00:14:48,200 --> 00:14:49,750
Perhaps it was Chairman Wu...

378
00:14:49,750 --> 00:14:50,600
Chairman Wu...

379
00:14:50,910 --> 00:14:52,480
I know him better

380
00:14:52,480 --> 00:14:53,480
than any of you.

381
00:14:54,440 --> 00:14:55,670
He truly cares for me.

382
00:14:56,750 --> 00:14:58,320
I would never betray him.

383
00:14:59,270 --> 00:15:00,750
Tomorrow is the Hero Gathering.

384
00:15:01,870 --> 00:15:02,750
It's too late.

385
00:15:03,550 --> 00:15:04,600
I'm going to sleep.

386
00:15:04,960 --> 00:15:05,800
Lingfeng...

387
00:15:18,720 --> 00:15:19,670
Master!

388
00:15:20,480 --> 00:15:21,750
Are you there?

389
00:15:23,200 --> 00:15:24,200
Tomorrow,

390
00:15:24,200 --> 00:15:26,320
I'll go to the Hero Gathering.

391
00:15:27,200 --> 00:15:30,200
I must get the hero token!

392
00:15:35,870 --> 00:15:36,790
This old man

393
00:15:37,240 --> 00:15:39,120
always fails me at crucial moments.

394
00:15:58,240 --> 00:15:59,600
My disciple

395
00:15:59,600 --> 00:16:00,720
is a good man,

396
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:01,960
but he's so foolish.

397
00:16:02,360 --> 00:16:03,200
Master!

398
00:16:04,840 --> 00:16:06,390
You freaked me out!

399
00:16:07,320 --> 00:16:08,270
You need a lesson.

400
00:16:15,360 --> 00:16:16,200
Master,

401
00:16:16,600 --> 00:16:18,550
tomorrow is my big day,

402
00:16:19,150 --> 00:16:21,080
but I'm so confused right now.

403
00:16:22,960 --> 00:16:24,240
Silly boy,

404
00:16:24,240 --> 00:16:25,360
why are you confused?

405
00:16:25,500 --> 00:16:26,370
Why don't you

406
00:16:26,390 --> 00:16:28,870
compete for the divine sect tomorrow?

407
00:16:29,150 --> 00:16:30,630
After all, I've given you the clothes.

408
00:16:30,630 --> 00:16:33,030
Master, stop teasing me.

409
00:16:33,030 --> 00:16:34,600
I'm really annoyed now.

410
00:16:35,120 --> 00:16:36,120
Everyone

411
00:16:36,120 --> 00:16:37,510
has their own ideas.

412
00:16:37,750 --> 00:16:39,670
My head is a mess.

413
00:16:39,960 --> 00:16:41,270
Listen,

414
00:16:41,270 --> 00:16:43,150
believe in yourself.

415
00:16:44,320 --> 00:16:46,670
There will be many variables tomorrow,

416
00:16:46,670 --> 00:16:48,000
but the only thing that's certain

417
00:16:48,000 --> 00:16:50,720
is that you'll get the hero token.

418
00:16:51,200 --> 00:16:52,390
Not for anyone else

419
00:16:52,390 --> 00:16:53,840
but for yourself.

420
00:16:54,510 --> 00:16:55,600
Understand?

421
00:17:08,150 --> 00:17:08,990
Master!

422
00:17:10,120 --> 00:17:11,000
Next time,

423
00:17:11,390 --> 00:17:12,870
let's change a place.

424
00:17:13,360 --> 00:17:15,640
It really stinks here.

425
00:17:31,510 --> 00:17:32,350
Yingdan.

426
00:17:33,640 --> 00:17:35,270
I'm really worried about you.

427
00:17:35,550 --> 00:17:36,440
Listen,

428
00:17:36,680 --> 00:17:37,830
if you can't win,

429
00:17:37,830 --> 00:17:38,750
don't push yourself.

430
00:17:38,750 --> 00:17:39,590
Got it?

431
00:17:40,160 --> 00:17:41,000
Got it.

432
00:17:41,960 --> 00:17:43,270
Where are Zhuge and Ling'er?

433
00:17:44,270 --> 00:17:45,110
No idea.

434
00:17:45,480 --> 00:17:47,310
I haven't seen them since morning.

435
00:17:47,310 --> 00:17:49,030
What a fair-weather friend.

436
00:17:49,640 --> 00:17:51,350
Luckily, I have you, Yingdan.

437
00:17:52,160 --> 00:17:53,750
Who's a fair-weather friend?

438
00:17:57,830 --> 00:17:59,720
Gou, you're going to the competition.

439
00:17:59,720 --> 00:18:00,620
You should eat more.

440
00:18:00,620 --> 00:18:01,590
Don't starve.

441
00:18:01,590 --> 00:18:02,680
You'll have energy after eating.

442
00:18:02,680 --> 00:18:03,720
I knew you wouldn't

443
00:18:03,720 --> 00:18:04,720
ignore me.

444
00:18:04,720 --> 00:18:05,560
Go away!

445
00:18:05,560 --> 00:18:06,440
