446
00:18:06,440 --> 00:18:07,480
(5 for 1 day, 9 for 2 days)
One!

447
00:18:07,480 --> 00:18:08,720
Buy your tickets here!

448
00:18:08,720 --> 00:18:09,750
Come here, sir.

449
00:18:09,750 --> 00:18:10,880
Do you need tickets?

450
00:18:10,880 --> 00:18:11,920
5% discount!

451
00:18:11,920 --> 00:18:13,110
This way, this way!

452
00:18:13,400 --> 00:18:15,070
- Over here!
- I'll take one!

453
00:18:15,070 --> 00:18:16,240
Miss, how many tickets?

454
00:18:16,240 --> 00:18:17,110
Just one.

455
00:18:17,110 --> 00:18:18,790
Are you with that lady?

456
00:18:18,790 --> 00:18:20,270
- Two tickets for a 5% off.
- No, just one.

457
00:18:20,270 --> 00:18:21,480
Line up here!

458
00:18:21,480 --> 00:18:22,640
Two tickets for a 5% off!

459
00:18:22,640 --> 00:18:24,200
- Do you need tickets?
- Just one.

460
00:18:24,200 --> 00:18:25,040
One ticket?

461
00:18:25,060 --> 00:18:26,200
- Okay.
- This way, please.

462
00:18:26,200 --> 00:18:27,040
Here you are.

