Lingfeng!

472
00:18:52,480 --> 00:18:53,830
You're so handsome!

473
00:18:53,830 --> 00:18:55,020
- Keep going!
- Lingfeng!

474
00:18:55,590 --> 00:18:56,590
Lingfeng!

475
00:18:56,590 --> 00:18:57,430
Got it.

476
00:19:02,790 --> 00:19:05,030
Why are there so few audiences?

477
00:19:06,030 --> 00:19:08,590
Maybe the tickets are too expensive.

478
00:19:08,960 --> 00:19:10,070
