481
00:19:19,110 --> 00:19:21,160
We live for justice!

482
00:19:21,160 --> 00:19:23,920
Today is the first day
of the Hero Gathering.

483
00:19:24,330 --> 00:19:25,920
(Hero Gathering Winner)
Let's stay tuned!

484
00:19:43,030 --> 00:19:43,880
Don't hit me!

485
00:19:52,680 --> 00:19:54,030
Why hasn't Master made a move?

486
00:19:54,640 --> 00:19:55,480
I don't know.

487
00:20:09,180 --> 00:20:12,980
(Deng Yunfeng, Gou Lingfeng)

488
00:20:45,200 --> 00:20:46,400
Great!

489
00:20:50,750 --> 00:20:51,790
It's all rigged!

490
00:20:52,030 --> 00:20:53,070
Shame on you!

491
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:56,030
(Deng Yunfeng, Gou Lingfeng)
We're entering the semifinals.

492
00:20:56,480 --> 00:20:57,640
The winner will compete in

493
00:20:57,640 --> 00:20:59,680
tomorrow's final for the hero token.

494
00:21:15,960 --> 00:21:17,720
Deng Yunfeng, the inspector of MAA,

495
00:21:17,720 --> 00:21:19,000
has won

496
00:21:19,270 --> 00:21:21,510
and made it into the final.

497
00:21:28,270 --> 00:21:30,590
Let's welcome Divine-Sword Knight!

498
00:21:33,750 --> 00:21:34,830
This is too much.

499
00:21:37,400 --> 00:21:38,310
This is a duel

500
00:21:38,310 --> 00:21:40,160
between Loyalty Knight from Huizhou

501
00:21:40,160 --> 00:21:42,070
and Divine-Sword Knight from Luzhou.

502
00:21:43,480 --> 00:21:45,200
The duel begins!

503
00:21:48,550 --> 00:21:50,960
May I ask your name?

504
00:21:51,960 --> 00:21:54,310
I'm Liu Yue,
Divine-Sword Knight from Luzhou.

505
00:21:54,880 --> 00:21:57,070
I've heard much about
the young and talented Loyalty Knight.

506
00:21:57,070 --> 00:21:59,510
I can finally spar with you today.

507
00:22:00,270 --> 00:22:02,400
My weapon is the Celestial Sword,

508
00:22:02,830 --> 00:22:03,790
and I've mastered

509
00:22:03,790 --> 00:22:06,240
the 26 styles of Celestial Swordplay.

510
00:22:06,790 --> 00:22:08,920
Looking forward to sparring with you.

511
00:22:10,480 --> 00:22:11,350
Loyalty Knight,

512
00:22:11,680 --> 00:22:12,640
please make your move.

513
00:22:21,880 --> 00:22:22,880
Guangming,

514
00:22:23,400 --> 00:22:26,550
I've heard Divine-Sword Knight
is a righteous man

515
00:22:26,550 --> 00:22:27,920
who never cheats,

516
00:22:28,200 --> 00:22:29,510
and his swordplay

517
00:22:29,510 --> 00:22:31,200
is also one-of-a-kind.

518
00:22:31,200 --> 00:22:32,750
It seems Gou Lingfeng

519
00:22:33,000 --> 00:22:35,920
will have a hard time.

520
00:22:36,550 --> 00:22:38,310
Without real abilities,

521
00:22:38,310 --> 00:22:39,920
you can't win

522
00:22:40,200 --> 00:22:41,880
in the Hero Gathering.

523
00:22:41,880 --> 00:22:44,400
I believe in Lingfeng.

524
00:22:45,480 --> 00:22:46,960
You can never

525
00:22:47,350 --> 00:22:49,030
foresee the result.

526
00:22:51,110 --> 00:22:52,000
Indeed.

527
00:22:52,200 --> 00:22:54,640
Let's wait and see.

528
00:22:56,220 --> 00:22:57,070
I think

529
00:22:57,070 --> 00:22:58,640
Gou Lingfeng is bound to lose.

530
00:22:59,260 --> 00:23:00,140
In the earlier rounds,

531
00:23:00,160 --> 00:23:01,510
he won by sheer luck.

532
00:23:02,070 --> 00:23:03,750
But Divine-Sword Knight

533
00:23:03,750 --> 00:23:05,240
is a famous hero.

534
00:23:05,240 --> 00:23:06,090
He won't go easy on him.

535
00:23:06,090 --> 00:23:08,070
Lingfeng, make your move!

536
00:23:08,070 --> 00:23:09,070
Don't disturb him.

537
00:23:09,070 --> 00:23:10,750
He's analyzing the opponent's weakness.

538
00:23:10,750 --> 00:23:12,270
You know nothing.

539
00:23:12,270 --> 00:23:14,480
Lingfeng is using his internal energy

540
00:23:14,480 --> 00:23:16,000
to battle with him.

541
00:23:16,000 --> 00:23:17,510
He also used this

542
00:23:17,510 --> 00:23:19,030
against All-Around Knight last time.

543
00:23:19,030 --> 00:23:20,680
It was impressive.

544
00:23:20,680 --> 00:23:21,750
Really?

545
00:23:24,270 --> 00:23:25,790
Why hasn't Master made a move yet?

546
00:23:25,960 --> 00:23:27,000
No idea.

547
00:23:28,350 --> 00:23:29,190
In that case,

548
00:23:29,440 --> 00:23:30,880
I won't hold back.

549
00:23:59,480 --> 00:24:00,350
Master!

550
00:24:00,350 --> 00:24:01,510
- What's going on?
- Great!

551
00:24:02,590 --> 00:24:03,590
Master!

552
00:24:04,270 --> 00:24:05,350
Keep it up!

553
00:24:05,350 --> 00:24:07,720
Lingfeng!

554
00:24:09,110 --> 00:24:10,440
Did he use demonic skills?

555
00:24:10,880 --> 00:24:11,830
Eunuch Deng,

556
00:24:12,110 --> 00:24:13,680
you've warned him.

557
00:24:13,680 --> 00:24:15,720
- He wouldn't dare use it.
- You...

558
00:24:22,780 --> 00:24:27,620
(Deng Yunfeng, Gou Lingfeng)

559
00:24:27,620 --> 00:24:28,700
(Deng Yunfeng)

560
00:24:28,820 --> 00:24:30,300
(Gou Lingfeng)

561
00:24:30,920 --> 00:24:32,400
Master, that was incredible.

562
00:24:32,400 --> 00:24:34,270
You made it to the final so easily.

563
00:24:34,590 --> 00:24:36,070
