564
00:24:36,070 --> 00:24:37,350
Divine-Sword Knight

565
00:24:37,350 --> 00:24:39,240
just lost on his own.

566
00:24:39,790 --> 00:24:41,550
What do you mean by "lost on his own"?

567
00:24:41,550 --> 00:24:43,030
That was my punch!

568
00:24:45,720 --> 00:24:46,680
We get it.

